data.description: Welcome to your future home in the heart of Florence, South Carolina - where classic charm meets modern elegance! This soon-to-be-listed gem features 4 bedrooms, 2bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, nestled in a well-established neighborhood that exudes Southern warmth. Crafted with a blend of brick and Hardi plank siding, this residence stands as a testament to enduring quality. Ascend to the second level to discover the master bedroom, offering a retreat of comfort and style. The convenience of a laundry room on the same level adds a touch of practicality, ensuring your daily routines flow seamlessly. An enticing bonus area beckons, promising versatility and potential for your unique needs. Each bedroom boasts its own walk-in closet, providing ample storage and a sense of personal space. Luxurious plank flooring graces the baths, kitchen, dining area, living space ,and a versatile flex room, harmonizing aesthetics with functionality. Situated conveniently near I-95, accessibility isa key feature of this residence, offering a gateway to both convenience and adventure. The stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen add a modern touch to the heart of the home.
